ize the quantum speedup in the amplitude estimation task.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Jun 2020 17:44:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Jul 2020 14:19:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 11 Oct 2021 12:23:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-12"}
