apolation. Finally, we estimate how this value will change as the\nlight-quark masses are lowered to their physical values.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Jun 2020 17:44:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 13 Jul 2020 21:52:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-28"}
