olution, SN 2018hti could originate from a massive, metal-poor\nstar with a zero-age main sequence (ZAMS) mass of 25--40 $M_\\odot$, or from a\nless massive rotating star with $M_\\mathrm{ZAMS} \\approx 16$--25 $M_\\odot$. For\nthe case of a binary system, its progenitor could also be a star with\n$M_\\mathrm{ZAMS} \\gtrsim 25$ $M_\\odot$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Jun 2020 00:39:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 16 Aug 2020 14:14:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-18"}
