r is equipped with a small\nnumber of RF chains and low-resolution ADCs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Jun 2020 09:43:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Jul 2020 09:25:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 12 May 2021 06:54:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-13"}
