advanced materials and growth processes, and constitutes an important step\nfor large scale fabrication of superconducting quantum circuits.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Jun 2020 14:52:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Sep 2020 12:13:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-29"}
